snippet.title: Meghan Markle's Friend Reveals Disturbing New Details About A Senior Member Of The Royal Family
snippet.description:
If you watched the interview Meghan Markle and Prince Harry gave Oprah Winfrey in March 2021, or watched the news coverage about it, you likely remember one of its biggest big bombshells. That being that an unnamed member of the royal family organization expressed concerns about how dark the skin color of Meghan and Harry's children would be.

The revelations from the interview continue to roil. For example, they seem to have led journalist Omid Scobie, a longtime friend of Markle's, to speak out about his own experiences with prejudice and the royal family on a British morning show. He revealed some disturbing new details about a senior member of the royal family.
